title: The Panorama Factory 5.3 Build 2800 m32 Edition
description:
The Panorama Factory 5.3 Build 2800 m32 Edition
The Panorama Factory creates high-quality panoramas from a set of overlapping digital images. You can add image hotspots, export to VR formats and create web pages that link your images into virtual tours. The software also corrects for lens-induced distortions and creates either cylindrical or spherical image projections. Additional features include onscreen zoom, support for digital SLRs, correction for barrel distortion, correction for brightness falloff and interactive controls.

*for Windows 98 / ME / NT / 2000 / XP / 2003 / x64 / Vista / Windows 7
*V5.3.2800 Released April 19, 2009
*NEW in V5.3:
*Supports WIC plug-ins for camera RAW on Windows!
*(requires Windows XP SP 3 or Vista or newer)

Tested with windows 7 x64, worked, enjoy!!!!
